messages.message: Hi @jack.robbins so I just realized ticket EPD-3775 (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3775) is past SLA. I went to the metrics page for this deployment and it doesn't look like the bug is there anymore? Can we close this as no longer applicable?
does it break for you with this link? https://aihub.instabase.com/deployments/01948f7c-e570-73c1-a63a-0dc578e47b7a/metrics?asOfTime=1741132612067&interval=30_days
Yeah I just went to the metrics page and clicked last 30 days
That one didn't work cause it's too far in the past

But I've played around with checking metrics history even farther in the past https://aihub.instabase.com/deployments/01948f7c-e570-73c1-a63a-0dc578e47b7a/metrics?asOfTime=1744000000000&interval=30_days and it seems to be working fine

Its a weird issue as I was able to replicate the "An unexpected error has occurred: Field missing" issue as recently as last week, but this also seems to have only happened on this deployment & for this customer. I'm okay marking it as closed & cant reproduce - we can reopen it if it occurs again for another customer.
